To run replay
1) populate YYYMMDDHH directory with symlinks to analyses, bias correction files
   and dtfanl.nc files.
2) put symlink for a single sfg*ensmean file in every directory (only used to
   get low res orography by adjustps.x).
3) set RES_CTL and replay_only in config.sh.
   adjust node counts processor layouts accordingly in gaea_preamble.
3) script main_replay.csh runs adjustps.x, run_gsiobserver and forecast.

